07182496a4359473a0465a7b","tid":408340,"uid":79859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想問BLT好唔好?</blockquote><br />\n唔好 但唔知點解成日排晒隊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有次好奇入去食 真係學上面個巴打話齋 笑而不語<br />\n最重要個餡可以接近0調味<br />\n牛味又唔出<br />\n仲要咁貴真係狗也不屌"},{"pid":"c9151b91fd5787447707521fc3674cd4da35fbb9","tid":408340,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>burgerman狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無問直接整well done比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nm記 signature好過佢<br />\n係個份量幾夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出名垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3dd483661f0e7da96a16bddc60cabf492416c1b","tid":408340,"uid":57827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Beef and liberty <br />\n講起又想食</blockquote><br />\nburger麻麻地<br />\nshake一流"},{"pid":"8b8ea5f93e2d4ef665c22b092119c5e7db09ddb0","tid":408340,"uid":19627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都想問BLT好唔好?</blockquote><br />\n唔好 但唔知點解成日排晒隊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有次好奇入去食 真係學上面個巴打話齋 笑而不語<br />\n最重要個餡可以接近0調味<br />\n牛味又唔出<br />\n仲要咁貴真係狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n個時樓下間BLT初初開 好好食 對佢好深印象 諗住佢呢間漢堡包都可以跟到下<br />\n點知呢間BLT burger 一開 我諗住都跟到下個水準 點知食完勁失望 <br />\n個時佢除左普通burger 外 其他都唔可以做combo 要a la carte <br />\n唔知而家重係唔係"},{"pid":"084c9c07c424b10b6212cb6f7cf3065316076ac5","tid":408340,"uid":33661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"e23d146bb78bc1fdb6d2c31fb3bb216587c7950b","tid":408340,"uid":114798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7305de07b18ee3b9f464d42709cfb50b720b42a9","tid":408340,"uid":27049,"li